msgstr "About us"

msgid "About.img_alt"
msgstr "Interior of "\"Mandrivna Kramnytsia\""

msgid "About.history_title"
msgstr "Beginning of the story"

msgid "About.history_text"
msgstr ""\"Mandrivna Kramnytsia\" was born in Podil — a place where trade routes and cultures have intersected for centuries. Here, among narrow streets, wooden benches, and the scent of spices, travelers from different parts of the world exchanged not only goods but also stories, flavors, and traditions. This very atmosphere of discovery became the foundation of our brand."

msgid "About.idea_title"
msgstr "Our idea"

msgid "About.idea_text"
msgstr "We took the spirit of ancient travels as a basis and brought it into modern times. Our shop is a place where every purchase turns into a small journey, and every product has its own story. Here you can find cheeses from France, spices from the Middle East, chocolate from Spain, or coffee from distant lands — everything that allows you to taste the world."

msgid "About.philosophy_title"
msgstr "Philosophy"

msgid "About.philosophy_text_p1"
msgstr "Our philosophy is simple: travel inspires, and every taste can open a new story. We believe that gastronomy is a universal language that connects people, cultures, and times."

msgid "About.philosophy_text_p2"
msgstr ""\"Mandrivna Kramnytsia\" is not just a place for shopping. It is a port for those looking for new emotions, who love to discover the world and find beauty in small things. We create a space where every visitor feels warmth, attention, and the atmosphere of a real journey."

msgid "About.fact1_title"
msgstr "10 years"

msgid "About.fact1_text"
msgstr "For ten years we have been collecting world flavors and conveying the atmosphere of travel in every product"

msgid "About.fact2_title"
msgstr "40 countries"

msgid "About.fact2_text"
msgstr "Our goods come from more than forty countries — from family farms to distant cultures"

msgid "About.fact3_title"
msgstr "1 shop"

msgid "About.fact3_text"
msgstr "One shop in Podil, but thousands of journeys inside. Each of our guests discovers the world in a new way"

msgid "About.fact4_title"
msgstr "8000 clients"

msgid "About.fact4_text"
msgstr "More than eight thousand travelers have already tried our products, receiving warmth, authenticity, and small discoveries"



